data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom pool home nestled in the tranquil Pineda Springs neighborhood with a breathtaking lake view. Step inside and be enchanted by the wood-look tile floors that exude elegance and charm throughout the open floor plan.  Enjoy the luxury of a summer kitchen, perfect for hosting outdoor gatherings. Take relaxation to the next level with the inviting hot tub.  For the connoisseurs, the bonus room boasts a humidor, ideal for preserving your treasured cigar collection. The kitchen is a chef's dream with granite countertops and gas appliances.  This home is an oasis of comfort and sophistication, a place where cherished memories are waiting to be made. Welcome home!
